casebody.data:
Alexander NOLTE
v.
Natalie Ann KANE.1 18-P-901 Appeals Court of Massachusetts. Entered: June 5, 2019

The modification judgment dated July 28, 2017, is vacated, and the case is remanded for further proceedings consistent with the memorandum and order of the Appeals Court. Until a new modification judgment enters, the father shall pay temporary child support of $830 per week.
